<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <% include ../partials/header.ejs %>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/home.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Quicksand&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <title>Home</title>
</head>

<body>

  <% include ../partials/nav.ejs %>

  <div class="container shadow-lg main-info rounded-lg mb-5 mt-5">

    <div id="carousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
      <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <li data-target="#" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#" data-slide-to="2"></li>
      </ol>
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
          <img class="d-block w-100" src="img/banner.png" alt="First slide">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img class="d-block w-100" src="img/screenshots/gameplay.jpg" alt="Second slide">
          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img class="d-block w-100" src="img/screenshots/results.jpg" alt="Third slide">
          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
      </a>
      <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div id="mainContent">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-5  col-md-12 col-sm-12 desc auto-align">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-info"></i> What is Tuning?</h3>
          <p>
            Tuning is a party game, where the players are groups of friends or strangers that compete against one
            another in a fast-paced game of guessing the song title, artist, or missing lyrics of the music clip that
            plays.
            Perfect for game nights with friends, trivia competitions, bars, and many more occasions. Also, gives you
            the opportunity
            to socialize and create closer bonds among friends or help you make new friends!
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-12 col-sm-12 auto-align">
          <img src="img/screenshots/playlist.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded">
        </div>

      </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider">

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-12 col-sm-12 auto-align">
          <div id="stepsPlay" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
              <li data-target="#" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
              <li data-target="#" data-slide-to="1"></li>
              <li data-target="#" data-slide-to="2"></li>
              <li data-target="#" data-slide-to="3"></li>
              <li data-target="#" data-slide-to="4"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
              <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="img/screenshots/signup.jpg" alt="First slide">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block" style = "background-color: black; border-radius: 6px;">
                  <h5>Step 1</h5>
                  <p>Create an account</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="img/screenshots/login.jpg" alt="Second slide">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block" style = "background-color: black; border-radius: 6px;">
                  <h5>Step 2</h5>
                  <p>Login</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="img/screenshots/gamemode.jpg" alt="Third slide">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block" style = "background-color: black; border-radius: 6px;">
                  <h5>Step 3</h5>
                  <p>Select game mode, single player or multiplayer</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="img/screenshots/gameplay.jpg" alt="Second slide" >
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block" style = "background-color: black; border-radius: 6px;">
                  <h5>Step 4</h5>
                  <p>Listen to the music clip</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="img/screenshots/answer.jpg" alt="Second slide">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block" style = "background-color: black; border-radius: 6px;">
                  <h5>Step 5</h5>
                  <p>Select/enter the right answer fast for more points</p>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#stepsPlay" role="button" data-slide="prev">
              <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#stepsPlay" role="button" data-slide="next">
              <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-12 col-sm-12 desc auto-align">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-info"></i> How do I play?</h3>
          <ul class="list-group">
            <li class="list-group-item">Step 1: Create an account</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Step 2: Login</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Step 3: Select game mode, single player or multiplayer</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Step 4: Listen to the music clip</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Step 5: Select/enter the right answer fast for more points</li>
          </ul>
          <!--<p>
            To play Tuning an account has to be created to play. Once you login, you can start playing
            right away with single-player and multiplayer modes. From there you can select which genre
            of music you want to listen and guess, and which type of mode you want to play: multiple
            choice, fill in the blanks, or voice input guessing. Once in the game, users will be given
            a limited amount of time to answer correctly. The faster you answer correctly the more
            points you can get! At the end of the game you'll be given a final score which will be
            recorded onto our leaderboards.
          </p> -->
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider">

      <div class="row">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-info"></i> Developers</h3>
      </div>

      <p>Here's the link to the <a href="https://github.com/bvtrinh/tuning">repo!</a></p>

